   Willmer, Pat; Matthews, Iain M., Univ St Andrews, Sch Biol, St Andrews KY16 9TS, Fife, Scotland.
   Stanley, Dara A., Trinity Coll Dublin, Dept Bot, Dublin 2, Ireland.
   Steijven, Karin, Wageningen Univ, NL-6700 HB Wageningen, Netherlands.
